    "description": "一部奇异有趣的叙事游戏，时长约3小时。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873440/extras/b1af0c9dcf3a63de0d4c2ffa27c7aeaa.avif?t=1727701026\" width=616 height=74 /></span><br>“我”有着两个身体：牛天赐非常自律，擅长学习；慕容蛋则喜欢自由。在“我”的伪装下，没人知道学霸和小混混竟然是同一个人。牛天赐学习时，慕容蛋需要去帮助处理琐事；慕容蛋闯祸了，需要牛天赐出来解决。<br>然而，少年的成长过程充满了矛盾：学业的压力，情感的懵懂，渴望理解却越发迷失，内心挣扎难以解脱……“我”会如何与自己相处？<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873440/extras/7806e492066ebc7aa53fcfb2335fecd1.avif?t=1727701026\" width=616 height=74 /></span><br>“我”需要控制屏幕两边的两个身体去做事和对话，内心独白会冒出在屏幕下方，有时需要完成互动和小游戏。<br>故事设定在十几年前的中国小城，重现了当年的校园生活。情节明快利落，对白幽默，剧情动画巧妙，每个环节都力求有趣。<br>荒诞的设定之下隐藏着触动人心的主题：人与自我。重返少年时代，你会与自己和解吗？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873440/extras/38b706302e676272d97269019432da5e.poster.avif?t=1727701026\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873440/extras/38b706302e676272d97269019432da5e.webm?t=1727701026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873440/extras/38b706302e676272d97269019432da5e.mp4?t=1727701026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873440/extras/c43ed6eae9b80b7dc50edc65d3635c11.poster.avif?t=1727701026\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873440/extras/c43ed6eae9b80b7dc50edc65d3635c11.webm?t=1727701026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873440/extras/c43ed6eae9b80b7dc50edc65d3635c11.mp4?t=1727701026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873440/extras/3df52d359f81eae71fb86c1eb4e1ec6d.avif?t=1727701026\" width=616 height=74 /></span><br>故事中的角色也是奇特有趣的。两个身体的反差非常明显：牛天赐，一本正经，但情商不高；慕容蛋自由散漫，不务正业。它们会在独白的控制下相爱相杀。<br>其他角色也都有符合自身个性的情节。例如：张狂是个放荡不羁的小混混，唯一在乎的就是兄弟义气；任老师追求排名第一，但面临坏学生的挑战，真实的性格也逐渐暴露……<br>接地气的台词金句频出，每个角色都是玩梗大师。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873440/extras/48c85d6a6fe1dfbbe1efd79143f2a316.avif?t=1727701026\" width=616 height=354 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873440/extras/9b85a1857e28c97294d4642d9ea437cf.avif?t=1727701026\" width=616 height=74 /></span><br>流程中包含约10个不同的小游戏，以及其他更小的互动。它们都是独特的叙事方式，为情节服务。<br>这些游戏都是快节奏的，难度不高，充满了趣味性。<br>* 当你要逃学去网吧，需要通关一个横版冒险游戏，<br>* 当你在走廊被班主任追赶，就转换为跑酷游戏，<br>* 当你在教室里拿粉笔扔同学，就会进入射击游戏……<br>其中一些游戏需要两个身体共同完成！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873440/extras/e09a485784329b06eece888a33bca0a3.poster.avif?t=1727701026\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873440/extras/e09a485784329b06eece888a33bca0a3.webm?t=1727701026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873440/extras/e09a485784329b06eece888a33bca0a3.mp4?t=1727701026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873440/extras/0283b2b904e3b505c64fd79e066aca5b.avif?t=1727701026\" width=616 height=74 /></span><br>数万字的台词全部都有配音，由最新的AI录制。以便提供更好的沉浸感。每个角色的嗓音都很有特色。<br>请注意：每一句都尽可能手动调整过了，但AI有时还是不能准确地表达情感。不适应的同学可以在选项中关闭配音。<br><br><i>* 这款游戏内需要阅读大量文字（有配音），不以战斗系统为主。<br>* 这款游戏包含脏话、未成年人叛逆（例如抽烟、饮酒、打架）、精神疾病等内容。</i>",
